Law enforcement sources tell TMZ ... the pilot who was flying Juice's private plane alerted authorities on the ground that the rapper's entourage had guns on them -- a big no-no in air travel. When they landed, FBI and FAA agents were waiting for Juice and company.
We're told at some point between the plane landing and the feds conducting their search ... Juice was seen swallowing several Percocet pills in what people believed was an attempt to hide them. Our sources say the pills might've contributed to his death in a possible OD.

I love juice wrld and his music but I been thinking that he could be faking his death and if he did die then there would've been at least one footage of him arriving at the airport or the hospital as he is famous and people are like that. Also the fact he done that tweet in the the previous year saying 'imma shine for a couple or years and fake my death' does kinda give the expression he faking it . And in one of his songs he said 'Im feeling like John Lennon' who was assassinated on 8th December. Not forgetting that TMZ mentioned the news about Juice wrlds death first and is saying 'There was Drugs on the plane'. All the evidence is coming from TMZ. No-one else is saying anything accept for TMZ. So it may be that TMZ partnered with Juice wrld. Also wait one more thing, everyone on tik tock before this was doing the 'Lucid dreams challenge' (search up on YT if dunno what it is) and they were pretending to have a seizure so Juice wrld might've thought bout this and used this idea too 'Fake His Death'. One more thing (sorrryyyy) but his family didnt really speak out on his death like nothing was said, his girlfriend didnt say anything. Ik its a hard situation if Juice wrld did die but like a picture/post would've made it official hes gone. But there was none of that.
Theres 2 things:
1. This could all jus be a massive coincidence
2. Juice wrld predicted his death
OR
He faked his death.
Am sorry if I do offend anyone but i'm speaking out about what I think. I love juice wrlds songs and when I found out about his death..... I couldnt believe it. I was searching up on YT on 'juice wrls death' and it was just upsetting. Seeing everyone saying 'He popped pills too save himself from going prison'. We should all just focus on Juice wrld and his happy moments. His songs were the best (again my opinion, sorry if thats not what you think) and I seen some disgusting things of people on YT saying 'Heres a video of juice wrld having a seizure' and when I click on the video theres a random person pretending too have a seizure. It makes me sick that this is what the world has come too. And if Juice wrld is actually dead then RIP❤️We love him with all our hearts ( Seeing as you searching up juice wrld on YT, I assume you like juice wrld too). And he was genuinely a good person in the heart.
Again If in 2 weeks Juice wrld says nothing about him faking his death then he probably has passed away.
But we'll never know. Theres two ways: It could be fake or real.
Am not gonna wait for 2 weeks tho as if he is gone then I would regret doing nothing and thinking hes alive.
So all my Prayers go too him and I hope he rest in paradise💗
We love you Juice Wrld❤️ RIP 🖤

I love juice wrld and his music but I been thinking that he could be faking his death and if he did die then there would've been at least one footage of him arriving at the airport or the hospital  as he is famous and people are like that. Also the fact he done that tweet in the the previous year saying 'imma shine for a couple or years and fake my death' does kinda give the expression he faking it . And in one of his songs he said 'Im feeling like John Lennon' who was assassinated on 8th December. Not forgetting that TMZ mentioned the news about Juice wrlds death first and is saying 'There was Drugs on the plane'. All the evidence is coming from TMZ. No-one else is saying anything accept for TMZ. So it may be that TMZ partnered with Juice wrld. Also wait one more thing, everyone on tik tock before this was doing the 'Lucid dreams challenge' (search up on YT if dunno what it is) and they were pretending to have a seizure so Juice wrld might've thought bout this and used this idea too 'Fake His Death'. One more thing (sorrryyyy) but his family didnt really speak out on his death like nothing was said, his girlfriend didnt say anything. Ik its a hard situation if Juice wrld did die but like a picture/post would've made it official hes gone. But there was none of that. 
Theres 2 things:
1.  This could all jus be a massive coincidence
2.  Juice wrld predicted his death
                       OR
He faked his death.
Am sorry if I do offend anyone but i'm speaking out about what I think. I love juice wrlds songs and when I found out about his death..... I couldnt believe it. I was searching up on YT on 'juice wrls death' and it was just upsetting. Seeing everyone saying 'He popped pills too save himself from going prison'. We should all just focus on Juice wrld and his happy moments. His songs were the best (again my opinion, sorry if thats not what you think) and I seen some disgusting things of people on YT saying 'Heres a video of juice wrld having a seizure' and when I click on the video theres a random person pretending too have a seizure. It makes me sick that this is what the world has come too. And if Juice wrld is actually dead then RIP❤️We love him with all our hearts ( Seeing as you searching up juice wrld on YT, I assume you like juice wrld too). And he was genuinely a good person in the heart. 
Again If in 2 weeks Juice wrld says nothing about him faking his death then he probably has passed away.
But we'll never know. Theres two ways: It could be fake or real. 
Am not gonna wait for 2 weeks tho as if he is gone then I would regret doing nothing and thinking hes alive. 
So all my Prayers go too him and I hope he rest in paradise💗
